    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab><persName ref="#people/214" key="#Bishops">Gherardus</persName>, gratia Dei
                        uius sancte Lucane ecclesie umilis <rs key="#Bishops">episcopus</rs>
                        concede, per cartula livellario nomine ad censum nobis perexolvendum (…), a
                                <persName><name>Adalberto</name></persName> filio <persName>bone
                            memorie <name ref="Adalbrandus">Adalprandi</name></persName>, id est
                        casa et res illa in loco ubi dicitut <placeName ref="#places/2108"
                            >Sacturno</placeName>, quas antea <persName key="#Agricultural_workers"
                                ><name>Ghaiprandulo</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Agricultural_workers">massario</rs> ad manus suas abuit, et tu
                        ipsi modo ad manus tua habere videtur, pertenentes <rs key="#Churches"
                            >ecclesie</rs> beati <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/1704"
                            key="#Churches">Sancti Petri de <placeName ref="#places/2105"
                                key="#Churches">loco Vicissimo</placeName></orgName>, quas ipse
                        eccl(esie) Sancti Petri est de subpotestatem ipsius <rs
                            key="#Mother_churches">episcopatui</rs> vestro <orgName
                            ref="#juridical_persons/68" key="#Mother_churches">Sancti
                            Martini</orgName>; casa vero ipsa cum fundamento et omnem edificio suo
                        seu curte, orto, ecc. (…). Censo (pro omni censum et iustitia): ad parte
                        suprascripte eccl(esie) per sing(ulos) annos per omne mense ianuario (…) ad
                        suprascripta eccl(esiam) Sancti Petri, per vos ecc. nobis vel ad
                        ministerialem nostrum, quas in ipsa curte et in ipsa eccl(esia) pro tempore
                        fuerint, argen(tum) solid(os) sex de bon(os) denarios espendibiles […],
                        duodecim den(arios) per sing(ulos) solid(os) rationatos; et per omnem Cena
                        Domini (…) ad suprascripta eccl(esia) uno pario pulli cum ovas decem; et a
                        mandato vestro ecc. (…). Pena: argen(tum) solid(os) triginta (…). <persName
                            key="#Writer #Notary"><name ref="Teudemundus"
                            >Teudimundus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs> scrive due <rs
                            key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis">cartulas</rs>. Actum <placeName
                            ref="#places/4" key="#Cities #Churches #Mother_churches #Bishops"
                            >Luca</placeName>. </ab>
                    <ab>Sottoscrivono come <rs key="#Witness">testimoni</rs>: <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Teobaldus">Teopaldo</name></persName>,
                            <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Albertus"
                            >Alpertus</name></persName>,<persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Iohannes"> Iohannes</name></persName>, <persName key="#Witness"
                                ><name ref="Stephanus">Stefano</name></persName>.</ab>
                </div>
            </div>
